
Common Use Cases
----------------
1. provision environments
   eliminate snowflake servers with provision/deployment from single source
   pre-made image preserved in a repository
2. configure operating systems
   post provision/deployment of hosts, modify kernel or major config files
   and add or remove or update packages
3. deployment of applications
   post provision/deployment of hosts, retrieve custom libraries or applications
   from a repository and deploy or update them to these hosts
4. perform compliance checks
   a. confirm valid TLS certificates
   b. confirm host network access restricted by a custom firewall
   c. confirm SSH access restricted to authorized users and applications
   d. confirm security tools installed
   e. confirm security patches installed by version, file size or timestamp
